# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# ============================================================
# Step 3. Collinearity + physical process-group experiment
#
# Goal:
#   Address reviewer concerns about VPD / Tair / Td collinearity,
#   and support interpretation using more physical process groups.
#
# Outputs:
#   1) correlation matrix
#   2) VIF table
#   3) reduced-model ablation table
#   4) grouped permutation importance table
#   5) city-level ranking stability table
#   6) publication-style figures
